every five years, eyes world turn china ruling communist party holds congress. event determines lead party. people go lead 1.3 billion people china - don't get say - helm world's second largest economy. 19th congress begin 18 october significant leadership changes expected current party leader chinese president xi jinping widely expected stay top job. mid-october, communist party china (cpc) delegates across china meet great hall people beijing. party 2,300 delegates - although 2,287 elected attend, reports suggesting remaining 13 delegates disqualified "improper behaviour". behind closed doors, cpc delegates elect powerful central committee, 200 members. committee turn elects politburo that, politburo standing committee chosen. china's real decision-making bodies. politburo currently 24 members, standing committee seven, although numbers varied years. vote, reality many people already handpicked current leadership, committee approves edict. central committee also elects party's top leader - general secretary - becomes country's president. is, likely continue be, xi jinping. 19th congress closely watched two main things. first, mr xi deliver lengthy report scrutinised analysts signs china's political policy direction next five years. secondly, politburo standing committee expected nearly completely refreshed. recent years, party set informal term age limits certain posts. politburo members expected step past informal retirement age 68. include wang qishan, head anti-corruption agency, although key xi ally may persuaded stay. mr xi premier li keqiang early 60s. would normally expect see new line-up future leaders presented public congress - including possible eventual successor mr xi - would take five years' time. however, speculation mr xi might break tradition time round delay step. it's likely there'll overall consolidation power mr xi. assumed unprecedented number positions since coming power 2012, including title "core" leader china, puts par past political giants like mao zedong deng xiaoping. likely allies placed leadership positions congress, may see enshrining policies, known "xi jinping thought", party charter. move would place level mao chinese political history. believe may even announce move would extend rule past traditional two-term limit presidency. since becoming president 2012, mr xi spearheaded sweeping anti-corruption campaign seen million officials disciplined. seen massive internal purge opponents. movement dubbed "the cult xi" also emerged, propaganda songs dedicated deluge positive press state media, coined nickname aimed endearing citizens - "xi dada", uncle xi. analysts believe major reshuffle standing committee could herald policy changes, large china would continue track, mr xi still helm ensure stability. home, china's five-year economic reform plan still play, mr xi's anti-corruption campaign growing authoritarian rule. china's push spotlight global stage, fronted mr xi, also expected continue. ranges controversial south china sea expansion one belt one road trade project, china's positioning alternative superpower compared us president donald trump. one tricky question remains north korea ongoing nuclear crisis. analysts believe china would continue hold back taking decisive action as, even congress, new leadership would still "mired internal debate" handle hot-tempered neighbour.
अमेरिकी राष्ट्रपति डोनल्ड ट्रम्पले आफ्ना समकक्षी चिनियाँ राष्ट्रपति सि जिनपिङले कम्युनिष्ट पार्टीको महाधिवेशनमा शक्ति संगठित गरेर पाएको 'असाधारण उचाइ' का लागि उनलाई बधाई दिएका छन्। कुनै स्पष्ट उत्तराधिकारी नभएपछि पुन: निर्वाचित भएका सिले अर्को पाँच वर्षका लागि आफ्नो पकड बलियो बनाएका छन्। उनको नाम र उनका सिद्धान्तहरु संविधानमा लेखिएका छन्। गत जुलाईमा जी-ट्वान्टी सम्मेलनमा भेट भएपछि अब अर्को महिना चीनमा हुने राजकीय भ्रमणका बेला दुवै नेताहरुले वार्ता गर्नेछन्। राष्ट्रपति ट्रम्पले ट्वीट गर्दै सिलाई बधाई दिएको र त्यसक्रममा उत्तर कोरिया र व्यापारबारे पनि छलफल गरेको बताए। ट्रम्पसँगको टेलिफोन संवादमा सिले अमेरिकाका राष्ट्रपतिसँग चीन-अमेरिकी सम्बन्धको भविष्यको विकासबारे संयुक्त रुपमा खाका बनाएर काम गर्ने इच्छा व्यक्त गरेको चिनियाँ सरकारी सञ्चारमाध्यमले जनाएका छन्। चीन अमेरिकापछि विश्वको दोस्रो ठूलो अर्थतन्त्र भएको मुलुक हो। जसको सबैभन्दा ठूलो व्यापारिक साझेदारी पनि अमेरिकासँग नै छ। यद्यपी, साउथ चाइना सी र इस्ट चाइना सीबारे बेइजिङ र इस्ट सीमा रहेका वासिङ्टनका समर्थकको क्षेत्रीय विवादका कारण यी दुई देशबीचको सम्बन्ध भने तनावपूर्ण रहेको छ। यसैबीच, उत्तर कोरियाको सरकारी सञ्चारसंस्था केसिएनएले त्यहाँका नेता किम जोङ-अनले सि लाई बधाईको सन्देश पठाएको बताए।
